1. *Slabo* sam spavao sinoć. (I slept *poorly* last night.)
2. On slabo razume engleski jezik. (*He* doesn't understand English *well*.)
3. Usporila sam tempo trčanja jer sam bila slabo pripremljena. (I slowed down my running pace because I was *poorly* prepared.)
4. Slabo mi radi internet već nekoliko dana. (My internet has been working *poorly* for a few days now.)
5. Slabo se vidim s tom osobom. (I *rarely* see that person.)
6. On slabo pazi na novac. (*He* doesn't *carefully* watch his money.)
7. Zainteresovan sam, ali slabo imam vremena. (I'm interested, but I *hardly* have any time.)
8. Učenik je slabo uradio na testu. (The student did *poorly* on the test.)
9. *Slabo* smo jeli ovaj vikend. (We ate *lightly* this weekend.)
10. Slabo se sećam šta se desilo. (I *barely* remember what happened.)